        "text": "The trespass-money and sin-money, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — “Besides the money paid to the priests for trespasses committed in holy things it is thought that persons living at a distance sent money to the priests to purchase trespass- offerings and sin-offerings, and sacrifice them in their names: and, as they commonly sent more than the sacrifices cost, the surplus became a perquisite, under the name of ",
