        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "trespass-money ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "sin-money.” — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Scott. This money was not employed toward the reparation of the house, because, as it follows, ",
        "children": []
